      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ舞台の本番ですね……\nドラマの撮影前とは、なんだか違った緊張感です",
      "startTime": 5.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "本番までにいろいろあったからなぁ……\n優があんなに演技に手こずるとは思わなかったし",
      "startTime": 13.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.3800908487
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも風邪で倒れちゃいましたね\n今はもう、どっちも完全復活しましたけど",
      "startTime": 21.1666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……面目次第もございません\nもう、あのような醜態は晒さないようにいたします……",
      "startTime": 27.8333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.7120180845
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、すみれは元々演技がうまかったけど\n今日までの間に、さらに磨きがかかったよな",
      "startTime": 35.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "そう言われるとなんだか照れちゃいますね\nうーん……本を読んだり、いろいろ勉強もしましたけど",
      "startTime": 43.8666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.2612469435
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんの看病をして\n本の内容を実感出来たのが良かったんだと思います",
      "startTime": 51.4333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.1932897012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん現実では、今回のアニメとか舞台みたいに\n不思議な力でぱっと病気を治せる訳じゃないですけど",
      "startTime": 59.3666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.5440154155
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "患者さんを見守って、元気になってくれた時は\nこんなに嬉しいんだなって分かったので",
      "startTime": 67.3333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.3571901084
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう。あの後、瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんにも\n{user}さんが倒れたことを話したんです",
      "startTime": 74.1666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんは慌ててお見舞いを持っていこうとしたので\n「もう治ってる」って止めたんですけど",
      "startTime": 81.0683312682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.2502740623
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんは……\n「惜しいことしたなぁ～」",
      "startTime": 85.9333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "「そんなん役作りにも生かせるし、おもろいし\n最高のイベントやん」って言ってました",
      "startTime": 92.7333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.6215474687
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "優のやつ、喉元過ぎればって感じだな……\n稽古中はあんなにどん底みたいな顔をしてたのに",
      "startTime": 101.5666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……経験を演技に生かすのは大事ということで",
      "startTime": 105.7590980452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.3173292718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "でも「おもろい」って言うくらいだし、優に看病して\nもらったら、寝込んでる間もからかってきそうだな……",
      "startTime": 114.8333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんはそんな子じゃないですよ\n病人をイジメて困らせるようなことはしません",
      "startTime": 121.7666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.2668964943
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "悪い悪い。……風邪は、俺のただの自己管理不足だけど\nみんなの役に立ったなら、良かったと思っておくよ",
      "startTime": 130.6666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.256873123
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、もう倒れるまで無理しちゃダメですからね\n夜に残業しなくてもいいように効率よく仕事して下さい",
      "startTime": 138.5333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.1333329518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "い、一番難しいことをおっしゃる……\n――あ。そろそろ幕が上がるみたいだな",
      "startTime": 147.1333329518,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3106.187446799993,
          "startTime": 146.0666662852
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.5273494324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよですね\n……それじゃあ、みんなを元気にしてきますね！",
      "startTime": 152.6666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
