      "text": "えへへ、まさかあの舞台を円盤化してもらえるなんて\nお客さんの応援あってこそですし、嬉しいですよね",
      "startTime": 163.4666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。あの舞台は、トリエルのキャラ再現度も\n凄かったって、評判が良かったからな",
      "startTime": 170.811070308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "それで、今日は特典映像の撮影なんですよね？",
      "startTime": 173.8664300521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 173.8664300521
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "舞台が終わって、この衣装ともお別れかと思いましたが\nまた着られて嬉しいです",
      "startTime": 181.9666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 184.1530811549
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "この衣装を着ると、困ってる人達を助けなきゃって\nなんだか張り切っちゃいますね",
      "startTime": 188.1999996185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "さすがすみれ、もう役になりきってるな\n俺も、すみれの手を煩わせないようにしないとな",
      "startTime": 194.3999996185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……",
      "startTime": 198.2541017454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 198.2541017454
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なんで、ちょっと残念そうにするんだ……？",
      "startTime": 200.0710631212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
